translations: 无形资产（intangible 的复数形式）

sentences.sentence: That approach fails to take into consideration intangibles such as pride of workmanship, loyalty and good work habits.
sentences.translation: 那种方法没有考虑无形的因素例如对手艺的自豪感、忠诚和良好的工作习惯。

sentences.sentence: There are intangibles one feels rather than sums up;
sentences.translation: 比所谓的总结更实在的是一些无形的感触吧。

sentences.sentence: Those are some of the intangibles that I hope people two years from now can claim.
sentences.translation: 那些是我希望两年后得到人们肯定的一些无形的事情。
